postcontent: Ask what you want for your property!!! I think it is our God given right to ask whatever price we as citizens want for our personal property. Over the years, I have bought and sold HUNDREDS of guns on AL. It has been a fun hobby and a great distraction from the day to day. I've gotten the opportunity to own so many types of firearms and meet other great enthusiasts that are like minded. Now I see the hysteria created by the loons who have no soul and kill randomly creating this madness we are in now. Some have capitalized off this lunacy by getting prices that would have been laughable 6 months ago. I am curious about something though. Is anyone buying right now?  I see a lot of inflated pricing, but am curious if there have been any takers. I am fortunate enough to have my collection pretty complete, and not in need of the crazy priced guns. If you have been able to get insane prices for your goods then I say good for you. I am not a hater, trying to ridicule you but am curious if there is a lot of posts with no sales or if there are buyers out there paying these prices.
